overview: Provocative, self deprecating and always one step ahead of the crowd, the consummate comedian that is Hal Cruttenden navigates the evils of the modern world, from over-sharing on social media and the 5:2 diet, to the perils of sexism and very real phenomena that is posh-boy guilt. There's never a dull moment in this effortlessly quick-witted set.
title: Hal Cruttenden: Straight Outta Cruttenden
